cc13","tid":932899,"uid":105094,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T06:59:11.000Z","msg":"屌你網都唔好上啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成撚日就係識罷買罷用抵制 <br />\n<br />\n咁多年淨係識依招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1986年，美國國家科學基金會建立了大學之間互聯的骨幹網絡NSFNET（英語：NSFNET），這是互聯網歷史上重要的一步。在1994年，NSFNET轉為商業運營。1995年隨着網絡開放予商業，互聯網中成功接入的比較重要的其他網絡包括Usenet、Bitnet和多種商用X.25網絡。<br />\n<br />\n1990年代，整個網絡向公眾開放。1991年8月，添&middot;柏納斯-李在瑞士歐洲核子研究組織建立了HTML、HTTP和最初幾個網頁之後兩年，他開始宣揚其萬維網專案"},{"pid":"5ee6c38104b29606cb0ac1ec54b03158c0a4e04a","tid":932899,"uid":54733,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T06:59:24.000Z","msg":"Microsoft APPLE Google<br />\n你有得唔用?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c95ac17148a6e4b834a2e826a969c8b302d6ded","tid":932899,"uid":22624,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T07:01:22.000Z","msg":"講到好似android 唔係美國嘅咁"},{"pid":"6493c4f96c1c1eae7587d6b4ea2adce03b80e43f","tid":932899,"uid":25424,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7c95ac17148a6e4b834a2e826a969c8b302d6ded","tid":932899,"uid":22624,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T07:01:22.000Z","msg":"講到好似android 唔係美國嘅咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T07:06:37.000Z","msg":"open source 人人有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同鳩鐵一樣<br />\n有一個中國人改左少少都自煮燃發"},{"pid":"70fe3df3f7a2e47aa03539cffdc756d32ee646a7","tid":932899,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T07:06:55.000Z","msg":"幾時唔好用cpu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a2d793d44ce22d58425cafa5bfb094221c02e1","tid":932899,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T07:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.g